Sunday /ˈsʌndeɪ, -dɪ/

(Sundays) 

1. N-VAR Sunday is the day after Saturday and before Monday. 星期日 

例： I thought we might go for a drive on Sunday. 我原以为我们可能星期日去开车兜风。

